dct_title_s: Map of south-eastern provinces of Madagascar, comprising part of the Tanala, Betsileo and Bara country from a sketch survey by the Rev. W. Deans Cowan
dct_description_sm: Boundaries and subdivisions of Tanala, Betsileo, and Bara territories are shown. Includes information on governance of various territories. Market towns and villages, forests, and forts and residences of Hova governor are shown. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 4 (1882), no. 9, pp. 521-37; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
